TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the table DIV_QUALITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT div_Quality.div_quality_Id as div_quality_Id, div_Quality.div_quality_code as div_quality_code FROM div_Quality with (nolock) WHERE div_Quality.division_group_id='gfs'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Sorts the data based on ORDER_NUMBER and INVOICE_DATE
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SRT_GROSS_MARGIN

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the table div_quality_xref
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DIV_QTY_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT div_quality_xref.hbi_quality_code as hbi_quality_code, div_quality_xref.div_quality_id as div_quality_id FROM div_quality_xref div_quality_xref with (nolock)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the XRF_ACCOUNT tbale
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_XRF_ACC_CHANNELDESC

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT LTRIM(RTRIM(soldto)) as soldto FROM XRF_ACC WHERE ts_div_cde = 'GF'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Fetches the records from the source table GFS_GROSS_MARGIN
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_GFS_GROSS_MARGIN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.TRANSACTION_CATEGORY, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.TRANSACTION_TYPE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INVOICE_NUMBER, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.ORDER_NUMBER, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.ORDERED_DATE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.ORDER_REQUESTED_SHIP_DATE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.ORDER_CANCEL_DATE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.SHIP_DATE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INVOICE_DATE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.PURCHASE_ORDER_NUMBER, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.CUSTOMER_NUMBER, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.SHIP_TO_ADDRESS_ID, TO_CHAR(GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.BILL_TO_ADDRESS_ID) AS BILL_TO_ADDRESS_ID, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INVENTORY_WAREHOUSE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.DECORATION_FACILITY, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.PRODUCTION_SUB_TYPE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.ITEM_COGS, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.SKU, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INVOICED_QUALITY_CODE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INVOICED_UNITS, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INVOICED_SELLING_PRICE, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.CONTIGENCY_EVENT, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.INCLUDE_IN_GROSS_MARGIN, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.GL_ACCOUNT_NUMBER_CS, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.GL_ACCOUNT_NUMBER_SL, GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.TRANSACTION_SOURCE_TYPE_ID, GFS_BI_STYLE_MASTER.BRAND_DESC FROM GFS_GROSS_MARGIN GFS_GROSS_MARGIN LEFT JOIN GFS_BI_ITEM_MASTER GFS_BI_ITEM_MASTER ON GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.SKU=GFS_BI_ITEM_MASTER.SKU LEFT JOIN GFS_BI_STYLE_MASTER GFS_BI_STYLE_MASTER ON GFS_BI_ITEM_MASTER.STYLE_ID=GFS_BI_STYLE_MASTER.STYLE_ID WHERE GFS_GROSS_MARGIN.BI_PROCESSED='N'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the table SLBA_FACILITY..
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY SLBA_FACILITY WHERE SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP = 'gfs'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the SLBA_ITEM to get the ITEM_ID
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.SKU as SKU FROM SLBA_ITEM SLBA_ITEM WHERE SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP='gfs'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the XRF_ACCOUNT tbale
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_XRF_ACC

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT XRF_ACC.SOLDTO as SOLDTO FROM XRF_ACC XRF_ACC WHERE XRF_ACC.TS_DIV_CDE = 'GF'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select fm.short_measure_name as short_measure_name, LTRIM(RTRIM(mg.GL_Number)) as GL_Number from financial_measure fm with (nolock) join Financial_Measure_GL_Xref_TSS mg with (nolock) on fm.measure_name_id=mg.measure_name_id

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To get GRP_CDE
